node.text: The ocean means a lot to me and I want to do my 1% in taking care of it. If we can all do our part we can protect it for the future generations! I’m happy to be working with @shiseido as they are a part of the #WeAreOneOcean campaign. #ShiseidoSBAS #ShiseidoBlue @wsl @wslpure @shiseido

node.text: Over my short time of traveling around the world I’ve learnt that it’s not about the places you go, but the cultures you experience, the people you meet. I met up with a few friends in Mexico last week and had a trip of a lifetime just enjoying the moment and the simple things in life. I’ve also learnt that trips aren’t dictated by the waves you catch but the memories you can bring back. At the end of the day, we are not just athletes/robots, we are human too! Grateful for the people I met and I wish I had more photos but most of the times I left my phone in my room 😂😶‍🌫️.
